Package: sfgov
Title: San Francisco Open Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for San Francisco Socrata Open Data portal (data.sfgov.org).
    Provides discovery, search, and data access for police incidents, 311 cases,
    fire incidents, budget, building permits, and more.
